Title: REST API: allow dots in pathnames through folder regexp
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: rest-api
Date: 1624373455
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.1.0b1

Previously folders with dots (.) in their filename were erroneously rejected
by the REST API. This has now been fixed, dots can now be used.

There is no further action necessary.
